Twitter Surpasses 1 Million Russian-Language Users, Yandex Says

-- B y   S c o t t   R o s e
-- 
2011-08-04T09:53:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-04/twitter-surpasses-1-million-russian-language-users-yandex-says.html
Twitter Inc.’s micro-blogging service
exceeded more than 1 million registered users in the Russian
language, Yandex NV, operator of  Russia ’s largest search engine,
said in an e-mailed statement.  About 370,000 messages in Russian are posted to Twitter
daily, Yandex said today, citing its own  research . Only 64,000
Russian-language users, or about 6.4 percent of all registered,
send tweets on a daily basis, the company said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Scott Rose in Moscow at 
 rrose10@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Balazs Penz at 
 bpenz@bloomberg.net . 